<br>
Though dmg absorbtion for Mages is a nice boost in power, they are really only used to thier full potiential while summoning mass amounts of Mod Rods on the next large raid, a role that most raiding Mages have come to accept . Unless its an AE group, I rarely get below 80% mana, and rather keep that on a leash in the event it is needed in a sticky situation - ergo not much use for Mod Rods. My grouping friends are well enough equipt that even the Cleric gets to throw nukes <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
